latestIgtvVideos.title: for long luscious and beautiful lashes.
My first dance video.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
At a tender age of 4 when kids can barely walk my mom had gifted me my first ghungroos. Sill remember how ecstatic and enchanted i was.  Since then my love started growing brick by brick. 
Had the privilege of performing at various esteem places infront of numerous esteem beings. The list is lenghty but the most indispensable would be , his Holiness, the Dalai Lama. Was unaware then how big a deal it was. 
The last time i had performed on stage was in class 10 (2010). Love never ceased but it kind of shifted grounds. In few years i started working and then  used to dance just for leisure. But after an extended interval of 11 years its time to rekindle and reconcile with this passion of mine. Mere thought is providing me immense happiness.

latestIgtvVideos.title: bungee jumping.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How long it takes to put forth an image of yourself to forget you are not the person you portray yourself as? 
I think this experience is always going to be a reminder for me that I am not the person as I am in my Instagram feed or my profession. But so much more and so much less than that. 
It was liberating.

latestIgtvVideos.title: bird's eye view.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Deep Blue silences.
No Earth below.
No Sky above.
Only Me.
My heartbeat.
My breath.
Such depth like this.
Such loneliness like this.
And me only me.
Now I believe I just don't exist.
I am alive.
